fields.name: FailureReason
fields.description: Failure reason when blob restore is failed.

fields.name: RestoreId
fields.description: Id for tracking blob restore request.

fields.name: Status
fields.description: The status of blob restore progress. Possible values are: - InProgress: Indicates that blob restore is ongoing. - Complete: Indicates that blob restore has been completed successfully. - Failed: Indicates that blob restore is failed.
